{"type": "article", "id": 64887, "title": "日剧《重版出来！》原著，关于漫画编辑部的热血故事", "description": "“书是翅膀，读书就会长出隐形的翅膀。”", "date": "2019-12-13T05:40:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 191, "name": "漫画"}, {"id": 50, "name": "日本"}], "category": 3, "author": 589058, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20191212124048dWsQIrKX8M0hVA9J.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">《重版出来！》</h3><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191212121825wgRAKIkC98NnhaMo.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.234783\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>内容简介</h3><p>小熊，因为伤病不得不放弃曾经的梦想，入职一家漫画杂志社，成为新人编辑。谁知刚入职不久就遇到杂志社的超级漫画家三藏山事件。</p><p>漫画家三藏山一心一意画了几十年漫画，却因为网民们对他尖锐恶毒的评价备受打击。被恶意刺伤的漫画家心灰意冷想要封笔。而小熊却注意到导致漫画画面变形的细节。最终，在编辑和助手的帮助下，三藏山重拾创作激情。</p><p>作为一个新人编辑的小熊，面对无数考验和危机交替袭来，元气满满的小熊拿出竞技时代的勇气和干劲，全力以赴冲了上去……</p><h3>作者简介</h3><p>松田奈绪子，当漫画家助手七年后在杂志《コーラス》（集英社）发表作品出道。代表作《重版出来！》《少女漫画》等。兴趣是跟猫咪玩和欣赏歌舞伎表演。</p><h3>译者简介</h3><p>赵婉宁，曾翻译过《重版出来！》、《新撰组异闻录》等日本漫画，《明日将至》、《杀死玛丽苏》等日本小说。</p><h3>书籍摘录</h3><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191212122846R1VOfWokJAUP402M.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.366577\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201912121229033cOYiNMdWz9mCtF0.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.388122\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191212122923oGy5UAHb4zJ1psRl.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.435294\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191212122939nZulMj8YPxfqk0gC.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502564\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191212122956STyZztC1vg6MEWIK.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.38000